<paragraph id="8BFD36D586076B21FECA84C5FDC9F626" blockId="21.[224,1209,2040,2493]" pageId="21" pageNumber="84">
Remarks. This species is easily confused in size and shape with other 
<taxonomicName id="4C424D5686076B21FD8384ABFBDAF69D" authority="" authorityName="Donald" authorityYear="1892" box="[603,1088,2271,2310]" class="Gastropoda" family="Murchisoniidae" genus="Stegocoelia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pleurotomariida" pageId="21" pageNumber="84" phylum="Mollusca" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Hypergonia">
